=  Inter-party Relations

​{!<span class="tooltip-text" title="United Australia Party">UAP</span>!}: [+ uap_relation : relationships +]

​{!<span class="tooltip-text" title="Communist Party of Australia">CPA</span>!}: [+ cpa_relation : relationships +]

​{!<span class="tooltip-text" title="Liberal Democratic Party">LDP</span>!}: [+ ldp_relation : relationships +]

​{!<span class="tooltip-text" title="Country Party">CP</span>!}: [+ cp_relation : relationships +]

​{!<span class="tooltip-text" title="Lang Labor">Lang Labor</span>!}: [+ ll_relation : relationships +]

​{!<span class="tooltip-text" title="Social Credit Party">SCP</span>!}: [+ scp_relation : relationships +]

